    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead">Worker Privacy Notice of Queen Margaret University </span></p>
<p><strong>1. What is this notice?</strong></p>
<div class="page">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p>This is the ‘Worker Privacy Notice’ of Queen Margaret University. Our contact details are: <a href="mailto:HRGDPR@qmu.ac.uk" title="HR GDPR Email Address">HR-Contact Email Address</a></p>
<div class="page">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p>We are a data ‘controller’, which means we are responsible for deciding how we hold and use your personal information. This notice explains how and why we will collect and use your personal information in the context of your engagement with us and your rights in relation to your personal information.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></Value>
